name: Homare Style LORA
description:
This is my first attempt at the Artist Homare

Not sure how it turned out... i tested the checkpoints and this i like this one.

Hope to hear your thoughts
It was trained over AbyssOrangeMix 2 Hard

All the preview images use

DPM++ 2M Karras 30 Steps 320x320 Hires x2 CFG 8 Denoising at 0.7

Recomended weight: 0.75

Thanks to AOM it does some NSFW
